[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe OSS-Fuzz log reports a heap-buffer-overflow in libexif’s function [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` when invoked by the `exif_from_data_fuzzer`. An attempt[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwas made to refactor `exif_data_load_data_entry`—changing its signature to accept [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madditional parameters [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`d`, `ds`, `total_ds`, `offset`, `i`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and inserting a [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CHECKOVERFLOW` guard. After applying the patch, compilation fails with dozens of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msyntax and undeclared‐identifier errors [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. “function definition is not allowed [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhere”, “use of undeclared identifier ‘total_ds’”, “fullds” undefined[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– During fuzzing, AddressSanitizer reports a multi-byte read heap‐buffer‐overflow [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat  [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  `exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m[39m` in `exif_data_load_data_entry`.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The crash trace shows `__asan_memcpy` reading past an allocated [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m‐byte buffer. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The code path is: `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` → `exif_data_new_from_data` → [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data` → `exif_data_load_data_content` → [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The patch replaces the existing `exif_data_load_data_entry` logic with a new [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msignature:  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```c[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  static int [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                       ExifEntry *entry,[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                       unsigned char **d,[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                       unsigned int *ds,[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                       unsigned int total_ds,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                       ExifLong offset,[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                       unsigned int i[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– It adds a `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` guard in place of two earlier bounds[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks and adjusts the call site in `exif_data_load_data_content` to pass `fullds`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i`, and `i`.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The patch also renames variables and restructures the code around offset [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputation.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPost‐patch compile log  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The compiler reports “function definition is not allowed here” at several brace [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocations, indicating that the new function signature was inserted inside another [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction’s body.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Identifiers `total_ds` and `fullds` are undeclared in the context where they are [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mused.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Indentation and brace mismatches [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“misleading indentation”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m further confirm that [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe patch disrupts the file’s existing function boundaries.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Hundreds of lines fail to parse after the misplaced function definitions, leading[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto a flood of errors.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– The surrounding context in **exif-data.c** around lines ~[0m[1;36m170[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m200[0m[39m: verify where [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` originally begins and ensure braces align if its [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msignature is to be changed.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– All call sites of `exif_data_load_data_entry`: confirm that parameters [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`d`, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ds`, buffer length, offsets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are declared and passed correctly.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Definitions and availability of the `CHECKOVERFLOW` macro [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor inline function[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand consistency of variable names [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`fullds` vs. `total_ds`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Nearby functions in the same source file to ensure the patch did not nest [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefinitions inadvertently.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m– Any header files or build scripts that declare `exif_data_load_data_entry` to [0m    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` function. A fuzz target [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtriggers a read of [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes past the end of a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap allocation, indicating [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmissing bounds checks when parsing EXIF entries.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch attempt was made to add an extra parameter [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`total_ds`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`, replace uses of the original buffer length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`size`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mundeclared identifier [0m[32m'fullds'[0m[39m`, revealing that the new parameter was neither [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclared consistently nor passed correctly in all call sites.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Function Signature and Calls**  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The definition of `exif_data_load_data_entry` and every invocation in [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif-data.c`. All calls must supply the new `total_ds` argument.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Buffer Length Parameters**  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Identify where the overall data size is known [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ds`, `fullds`, or similar [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariables[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and ensure it’s passed to deep parsing routines.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Macro or Inline Function for Overflow Checks**  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm `CHECKOVERFLOW` is defined, imported, and behaves as expected.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Recursive and Loop Logic in `exif_data_load_data`**  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Examine how nested IFD entries are iterated and recursed into; ensure accurate[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtracking of the remaining buffer length.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Error Logging and Early Exits**  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify that any return paths on sanity check failures free or unref resources [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly and don’t leave the code in an inconsistent state.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy reviewing these areas, one can ensure bounds checking is consistently applied [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand fix the compilation break introduced by the patch attempt.[0m                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibexif/exif-data.c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, triggered by a malformed input [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min a fuzzing harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The overflow occurred at a `memcpy`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes just past the end of a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte allocation. [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch attempt modified `exif_data_load_data_entry` to add a new parameter [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`total_ds`, replaced previous size checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`size` and `offset`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with checks against[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`total_ds`, and introduced a `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` guard. After [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying the patch, the same heap-buffer-overflow is still reported at the same [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocation in `exif_data_load_data_entry`.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer invokes `exif_data_new_from_data`, which calls downstream functions[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincluding `exif_data_load_data` and `exif_data_load_data_entry`.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - AddressSanitizer reports a multi-byte read overflow in `__asan_memcpy` at line[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m of `exif-data.c`.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The offending copy reads [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes at address `[0m[1;36m0x51100000024f[0m[39m`, which is [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexactly one byte past a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap buffer.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack trace highlights:  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `exif_data_load_data_entry` → `exif_data_load_data_content` → [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data` → `exif_data_new_from_data` → fuzz harness.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The shadow-byte map confirms the overflow is immediate past the allocated [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregion.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Signature of `exif_data_load_data_entry` extended with `unsigned int [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal_ds`.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Removed old checks:  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` replaced by `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` replaced by `if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Call sites updated to pass the data-section size `ds` as `total_ds`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Log messages adjusted to refer to `total_ds`.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Example of patched snippet:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     static int[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     exif_data_load_data_entry [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, ExifEntry *entry,[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                const unsigned char *d,[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                unsigned int size, unsigned int offset,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                unsigned int total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         unsigned int s, doff;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[33m...[0m[39m compute s, doff [0m[33m...[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Guard against reading past the end *[0m[35m/[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Tag starts past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, doff, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, doff + s, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Proceed with [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + doff, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer for [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m runs, the same sanitizer [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrash at the same code location occurs.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Observations & Investigation Targets  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow remains in `exif_data_load_data_entry`, suggesting the current [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mguard conditions do not cover the failing scenario.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The values of `doff`, `s`, and `total_ds` in the failing input should be [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogged or inspected to understand why `CHECKOVERFLOW` did not trigger.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Investigate how `size` vs. `total_ds` differ in the context of content [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Does `size` represent the entire buffer while `total_ds` is only the TIFF [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata section?  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Are there code paths where `total_ds` is smaller than the region being [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maccessed but not checked?  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Audit related functions for consistent bounds usage:  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `exif_data_load_data_content` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcalculates offsets for individual entries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `exif_data_load_data` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreads IFD offsets and entry counts[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Loop logic around nested IFDs and offsets computed as `offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * i`  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify the definition and semantics of `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensure it correctly detects all out-of-bounds cases [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., zero-length buffers or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvery large `s`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Examine any assumptions about structure sizes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m-byte header, [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and ensure they cannot be subverted by a crafted input.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m467[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mCHECK_REC [0m[1;39m([0m[39mEXIF_IFD_EXIF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39md, ds, o,[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m469[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mrecursion_cost + [0m[1;35mlevel_cost[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m499[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mdefault:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m500[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:952[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m960[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m952[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* The JPEG APP1 section can be no longer than [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m KiB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding a[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m953[0m[39m:    [0m[39m   [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-bit length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so cap the data length to protect against overflow[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m954[0m[39m:    [0m[39m   in future offset calculations *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m955[0m[39m:    [0m[39mfullds = ds;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m956[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mds > [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m957[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mds = [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m958[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m959[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Byte order [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, length [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m960[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!memcmp [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, [0m[32m"II"[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:843[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m851[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m843[0m[39m:void[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m844:e[0m[39mxif_data_load_data [0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, const unsigned char *d_orig,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m845[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m     unsigned int ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m846[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m847[0m[39m:    [0m[39munsigned int l;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m848[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifLong offset;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m849[0m[39m:    [0m[39mExifShort n;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m850[0m[39m:    [0m[39mconst unsigned char *d = d_orig;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m851[0m[39m:    [0m[39munsigned int len, fullds;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:984[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m990[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m984[0m[39m:    [0m[39mexif_data_load_data_content [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_0, d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, ds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, offset, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m985[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m986[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* IFD [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m offset *[0m[35m/[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m987[0m[39m:    [0m[39mn = exif_get_short [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + offset, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m988[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* offset < [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m<<[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m, n is [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bit at most, so this op will not overflow *[0m[35m/[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m989[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * n + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m990[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root‐cause analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – The heap‐overflow in exif_data_load_data_entry is the result of using the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*capped* TIFF data length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ds`, which was munched to [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[39m or to `ds-[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m` after [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipping the [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m‐byte header[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m for entry‐level memcpy bounds checking.  In reality the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer supplies a buffer of N bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[39min the repro, [0m[33mN[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m207[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and after “skip‐[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m” you [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mget a [0m[1;36m201[0m[39m‐byte region for directory parsing.  However, in malformed entries the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode still uses that *[0m[1;36m201[0m[39m* as the upper limit for the actual data copy, even though[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe *real* buffer you can safely read from is the *full* [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m bytes.  That [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moff‐by‐“[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m” discrepancy allows a crafted tag to slip past the “size – doff” guard [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand read [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes starting at the one‐past‐end of the [0m[1;36m201[0m[39m‐byte region [0m[1;39m([0m[39maddress [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m0x[0m[39m…24f[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, even though the true buffer is [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m long.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – The prior patch only added a `total_ds` parameter but continued to pass the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshrunken `ds` into it, so the guards remained ineffective.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High‐level patch approach  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Carry the *full* TIFF‐section length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m“fullds”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m through all of the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*entry‐level* boundary checks, while still capping `ds` for *directory* parsing.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. To do this:  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • In `exif_data_load_data`, capture the original incoming `ds` in `fullds` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand leave `ds` free to be capped to [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[39m if desired for directory‐table safety.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Change **both** calls to `exif_data_load_data_content` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe primary IFD0 [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand the IFD1 branch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to pass *two* lengths:  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          – `dir_ds   = ds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m`            [0m[1;39m([0m[39mused for parsing IFD counts and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffsets[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          – `full_ds  = fullds - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m`        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mused for entry‐level memcpy guards[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Modify `exif_data_load_data_content` to accept a new `unsigned int full_ds`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparameter, propagate it on every recursive call, and hand it to [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Adjust `exif_data_load_data_entry`’s signature to accept `unsigned int [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal_ds` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e. the `full_ds`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and use it in:  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          - `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m … return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          - `if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m … return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed steps  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. **In exif-data.c** around line [0m[1;36m940[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `exif_data_load_data`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```diff[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       unsigned int ds_cap, fullds;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* original:      fullds = ds;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mds > [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ds = [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       fullds  = ds;         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* keep the true fuzzer‐supplied length *[0m[35m/[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ds_cap  = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mds > [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ? [0m[1;36m0xfffe[0m[39m : ds;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* call for IFD0 *[0m[35m/[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   -   [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_0, d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, ds_cap - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, offset, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +   [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                               EXIF_IFD_0,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                               d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                               ds_cap - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* directory ds *[0m[35m/[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                               fullds  - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* full ds for data copies *[0m[35m/[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                               offset,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                               [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* existing IFD1‐offset check uses ds_cap… *[0m[35m/[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   -  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * n + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > ds_cap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m * n + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > ds_cap[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* call for IFD1 *[0m[35m/[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   -  [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_1, d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, ds_cap - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, offset1, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +  [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata,[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                              EXIF_IFD_1,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                              d + [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                              ds_cap - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                              fullds  - [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                              offset1,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   +                              [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. **Modify** `exif_data_load_data_content` signature [0m[1;39m([0m[39mat its definition[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m from  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      void [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      ExifIfd    ifd,[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      const unsigned char *d,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int ds,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int offset,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int recursion_cost[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      to[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      void [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data,[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      ExifIfd    ifd,[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      const unsigned char *d,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int dir_ds,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int total_ds,[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int offset,[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                      unsigned int recursion_cost[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. **Inside** `exif_data_load_data_content`, wherever you see  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, ds, [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m …[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* later *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, ds, [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*n[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m …[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      replace those uses of `ds` with `dir_ds`, *leaving* the checks coercing the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory‐table to the capped region.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. **Propagate** the new `total_ds` on every recursive call [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcases [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEXIF_IFD_EXIF, EXIF_IFD_GPS, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, e.g.:  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```diff[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_EXIF, d, ds, o, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion_cost+[0m[1;35mlevel_cost[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      + [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, EXIF_IFD_EXIF, d, dir_ds, total_ds, o, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion_cost+[0m[1;35mlevel_cost[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. **Update** the single call to `exif_data_load_data_entry` in this function [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, entry, d, ds, offset+[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*i[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      to[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```c[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, entry, d, dir_ds, offset+[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m*i, total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. **Adjust** the signature of `exif_data_load_data_entry` to receive `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsigned int size, unsigned int offset, unsigned int total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and use `total_ds` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min both bounds checks:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```diff[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - static int[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, unsigned int size, unsigned int offset[0m[1;39m)[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      + static int[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      + [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, unsigned int size, unsigned int offset,[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      +                            unsigned int total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```diff[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* replace the two uses of “size” in the sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      + if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= total_ds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      + if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, total_ds, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why this works and preserves functionality  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – **Directory parsing** still uses a capped `dir_ds` to guard against [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpathological JPEG‐segment overflows.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – **Entry‐level data** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe actual memcpy[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is now clamped by `total_ds`, which [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis the real number of bytes available beyond the [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m‐byte TIFF header.  No more [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moff‐by‐[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m underreads.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – All existing logic—formats, recursion guards, integer‐overflow detection in `s[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m= [0m[1;35msize_of[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * components`—remains in place.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Only the *size parameter* to `exif_data_load_data_entry` has been decoupled [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom the *directory size*, restoring it to the true buffer length for memcpy.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side‐effect analysis & mitigation  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – The new parameters are purely internal to the two functions; no public API or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests change.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – Recursive calls to content/entry are updated consistently so no hidden code [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath slips through.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – We preserve the capped‐DS safety net for endless IFD tables while ensuring [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlegitimate read areas are correctly bounded.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – No harness or test code modifications are needed; existing regressions or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzer usage will still invoke `exif_data_new_from_data` unchanged.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
